==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Brigue
<hw>Brigue</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>briguer</ets>. See
<er>Brigue</er>, <pos>n.</pos>]</ety> <def>To contend for; to canvass;
to solicit.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Bp. Hurd.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

